{"tid":1223570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大哲學系教職員：嚴正譴責香港政府及警察武力鎮壓和平示威","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:34:51.000Z","uid":128923,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"508ddd8c179c1ea88de3d4d410e073736f9409db","tid":1223570,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"嚴正譴責香港政府及警察武力鎮壓和平示威<br />\n<br />\n茲就6月12日香港警察於金鐘一帶以殘暴手段和過分武力對待市民，及特首林鄭月娥就此事之回應，我們以聯署方式發佈聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n當天絕大多數示威人士以和平合理方式，行使其集會示威之權利，惟政府及警方竟將示威定性為「暴動」；其鎮壓之嚴厲及殘忍，更是前所未見，包括使用催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈，毫無預告、無差別地直接正面射向大批年輕學生、市民大眾，甚至記者。此等過分之暴力行徑，麻木不仁，我們予以最嚴厲之譴責。<br />\n特首林鄭月娥接受電視訪問時，將政府人民喻為母子，所言令人憤慨。從政者&mdash;&mdash;尤其一地之首長&mdash;&mdash;自比為民眾父母，高尊在上，已有違現代政治倫理；既為人父母，又何忍對子女作如斯無情之鎮壓及傷害？此種令人髮指之行徑，更甚於豺狼。<br />\n際此非常時期，同學勇於追求公義，我們深表欽佩，並盼諸位注意人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n香港中文大學哲學系一群教職員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/web/zh-hant/strongly-condemn-the-hong-kong-sar-government-and-the-police-for-suppressing-peaceful-demonstration-with-excessive-force/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Fzh-hant%2Fstrongly-condemn-the-hong-kong-sar-government-and-the-police-for-suppressing-peaceful-demonstration-with-excessive-force%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8M2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=22bc9a56\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.phil.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/web/zh-hant/strongly-condemn-the-hong-kong-sar-government-and-the-police-for-suppressing-peaceful-demonstration-with-excessive-force/</a>"},{"pid":"2b55d0db4b1ab3ce583c7c868649f13c83cbe782","tid":1223570,"uid":128923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:38:59.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"d7084ff8d65b56c15813018eb57699ea20723912","tid":1223570,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5b320832182b83ed875b06ffc2d5bcfa21efb4","tid":1223570,"uid":50457,"like":0,"d